para_sentences.para_0: There's an error in this video.  At 3:10, I accidentally typed "nums" instead of "nums_L".  In a previous take of the video, I had used the name "nums" for the list, and when I did another take, I cleared the console screen, but that didn't clear the memory.  The error makes it look like the value 10 got appended to the list before the append command was executed.
